page.title: 20Cubs
page.content:
Cubs
We have to be in the scout hut by 6 o'clock every Tuesday. First we have Grand Howl in which we lower the flag and salute it then Arkela lowers her arms and we have to crouch down and say "Arkela we will do our best". After tnat we have inspection where the sixer checks your pack, your neckerchief and sees that your hands are clean. After that we have to give in our testwork if we have got any or we do something with the rest of the six _ like playing games, tracking or doing some knotting. Last week we went to visit the police station. At the end of the evening we have another Grand Howl and some prayers and then we go home at half past seven.
